Module QemuJuicy
Package qemujuicy

Class QemuSetup

  • java.lang.Object
    • qemujuicy.QemuSetup
  • public class QemuSetup
extends Object
    QEMU setup of the application, looking for a valid QEMU installation. This could also be a fresh install. The values of this setup are stored for the settings dialog.
